We’ve fallen in love 💕 say “I do” to the Lulus Spring Bridal Collection to find the wedding wardrobe of your dreams. Shop the collection now, featuring new styles, colors, and sizes up to 3X. 🌸 
This spring, take a walk to remember in a wedding dress that's utterly unforgettable. Choose a bridal style that's undeniably you, whether that's a body-skimming lace gown or an organza strapless confection with origami pleats. From sleek and modern silhouettes in clean, solid white to glam gowns with sequins and beading, there's a wedding-ready look that's just well, meant to be yours. 
To help illustrate your love story, outfit your bride tribe in dresses that are as special as they are. Vintage-inspired hues like blush, pale blue, and sage are soft and romantic. Navy is elegant and timeless. Muted metallic sequins dazzle in an understated way. Mix it up with mismatched bridesmaid styles, or keep things simple with one dream dress for all of your lovelies. Either way, with Lulus' spring bridal collection, it's going to be a beautiful day. Next stop: forever. #lovelulus #lulusweddings

Make holiday magic this season in a festive look that will land you at the top of the best-dressed guest list. Whatever the RSVPs on your calendar, party pieces in timeless colors will ensure this is your time to shine. Sparkle in a silver sequin mini dress, amp up a cozy black sweater with metallic pants, or dazzle in ultra-glittery extras like rhinestone boots, belts, and hair clips. Winter whites are hotter than ever for holiday, so whether you're headed to a family gathering or a New Year's Eve bash, you've got plenty of en-blanc options like a leopard print puff-sleeve dress, satin one-shoulder frock, shimmery sequin top, or knee-high boots. Feel free to add un-basic black into the mix, too. Keep it cocktail-chic in a strapless black and white sheath, opt for an upgraded LBD with sheer sleeves, or dial up the drama by adding tall black boots to a printed daytime dress (office party, anyone?). With styles ranging from sequin bodycons to satin slip dresses, your holiday wish list starts right here.
